OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780675876
OL,3,CRapist to be sentenced after wrongful
OL,4,C17 year conviction of man
OL,6,FA sex offender who evaded justice for
OL,7,Fmore than two decades will be
OL,8,Fsentenced for the rape of a woman in
OL,9,Fan attack that led to the wrongful
OL,10,Fconviction of another man who spent 17
OL,11,Fyears in prison.
OL,13,FPaul Quinn was found guilty of two
OL,14,Fcounts of rape, one count of choking
OL,15,Fwith intent and one count of grievous
OL,16,Fbodily harm after new DNA technology
OL,17,Flinked him to the crime.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
