PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780675876
OL,3,CRapist to be sentenced after wrongful
OL,4,C17 year conviction of man
OL,6,FThe victim, who cannot be named for
OL,7,Flegal reasons, was walking along
OL,8,FCleggs Lane in Little Hulton, near
OL,9,FSalford, in the early hours of 19 July
OL,10,F2003 when she was dragged down an
OL,11,Fembankment and attacked by Quinn.
OL,13,FDuring the trial, the victim gave
OL,14,Fevidence and told the court her last
OL,15,Fmemory before being strangled
OL,16,Funconscious was a man on top of her
OL,17,Fwith his hands around her neck.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780675876
OL,3,CRapist to be sentenced after wrongful
OL,4,C17 year conviction of man
OL,6,FAfter an e-fit based on a description
OL,7,Fof the attacker was produced by
OL,8,Fpolice, Andrew Malkinson was picked
OL,9,Fout of a digital identity parade by
OL,10,Fthe victim and two other witnesses -
OL,11,Fdespite no DNA evidence linking him to
OL,12,Fthe crime.
OL,14,FMr Malkinson served 17 years behind
OL,15,Fbars for a crime he did not commit.
OL,16,FNow aged 60, he was only released in
OL,17,F2020 after 17 years in jail, with his
OL,18,Fconviction finally quashed by the
OL,19,FCourt of Appeal in 2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780675876
OL,3,CRapist to be sentenced after wrongful
OL,4,C17 year conviction of man
OL,6,FQuinn, of Exeter, Devon, and formerly
OL,7,Fof Little Hulton, Salford, always
OL,8,Fdenied any involvement in the brutal
OL,9,Fattack and was never linked to the
OL,10,Fcrime until 2022 when new evidence
OL,11,Femerged.
OL,13,FFollowing a six-week trial at
OL,14,FManchester Crown Court, Quinn was
OL,15,Fconvicted of two counts of rape.
OL,17,FHe was also convicted of causing
OL,18,Fgrievous bodily harm and attempting to
OL,19,Fchoke or strangle his victim to render
OL,20,Fher unconscious while he carried out
OL,21,Fthe attack.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
