FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780675876
OL,3,CRapist to be sentenced after wrongful
OL,4,C17 year conviction of man
OL,6,FFallout from the case includes a
OL,7,Fpublic inquiry which is now under way
OL,8,Fafter a 2024 review found failings
OL,9,Fthat could have exonerated Mr
OL,10,FMalkinson a decade before he was
OL,11,Feventually released from prison.
OL,13,FFive former Greater Manchester Police
OL,14,Fofficers and one currently serving
OL,15,Fwith the force are under investigation
OL,16,Fby the Independent Office for Police
OL,17,FConduct (IOPC) with both the chair and
OL,18,Fchief executive of the Criminal Cases
OL,19,FReview Commission (CCRC) having
OL,20,Fresigned.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
